Package com.jedago.practica_dss.core

Class Order

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jedago.practica_dss.core.Order
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<OrderLine>
    public class Order
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<OrderLine>, java.io.Serializable
    A class to represent an order placed in the cafe class. The order is determined by a id, a list of OrderLine, a total price of the order and an opening date.
    Version:
    1.0. 21/03/2021
    Author:
    Gonzalo Ulibarri
